Artisan Coin, A Fresh New Height on Coin Gaffs.
In addition to performing the regular routines with a shell set, the Ancient Chinese Coin set can also be used to perform the Shelled version of the CCC. This results in a simpler and very clean handling of the routine.
- Made of high-quality brass;
- Four coins, and one shell;
- Dollar size;
- Dean Set method, (unexpanded shell); high closeness and full coverage;
- Chamfered edges treatment for more comfortable handling;
- Fully polished but can be aged via DIY. Included are instructions to age the coin;
- Online instructional video for the Shell version of CCC & a ribbon are included.
[The instructions are meant to be sold separately as individual downloads afterwards.]
The price is only on KickStarter.
INCLUDES:
Chinese Coin Shell Set (Dollar Size, Unexpanded, Chamfered)
Online Instructional Video (only free on Kickstarter)

updates.update_content:
Hey Dungeoneers,
The Dark Dungeons DVD is almost ready to go to print!  Everyone should have filled out and returned their survey which asked how you wanted your name to appear on the DVD.  Those answers have been put in a spreadsheet and are about to be locked in. 
If you haven't sent in your survey yet then you need to;

Hi Dungeoneers!

The final Dark Dungeons trailer can be found on our webpage;
http://darkdungeonsthemovie.com/
As well linked to in this article in Wired;

And here it is, the moment you have been waiting for, the very first trailer for DARK DUNGEONS THE MOVIE;
http://on.fb.me/1cSc4gj 
Please share this far and wide!  It's really hard to get news about small projects like this out, so we absolutly depend upon the support of fans like you to spread the word.  If you would take five seconds to share this link
